methods.makeAggregationContext:
Make an AggregationContext for this aggregation.

:param table: (io.deephaven.engine.table.Table) - The source Table to aggregate
:param groupByColumns: (java.lang.String...) - The key column names
:return: (io.deephaven.engine.table.impl.by.AggregationContext) A new or safely reusable AggregationContext

text: Produces an AggregationContext for aggregations given a table and the names of the group by columns.
